{"tid":1359442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋推post可唔可以唔好淨係打個推字","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:09:27.000Z","uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"338e02f1502190cb2c5f53a33ad1d4a159308e61","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"見到而家愈嚟愈多post提返起721班黑警嘅惡行<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得好！冇做錯！</span></span><br />\n但我可唔可以拜託你哋推post嘅時候<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以唔好淨係打個push/推字呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n之前有巴打提過用「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我冇嘢講</span></strong>」咁去推<br />\n成功提醒一眾巴打被捕時唔需要同班黑警講任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你哋推721/白衫post嗰時<br />\n用返五大訴求/光復香港口號去推post得唔得呀？<br />\n咁就夠架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊用五大訴求推post！唔好再做懶人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n 6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deea00d580236a142e847888e02da5ea9738f14e","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"唔想再喺啲post到淨係見到你哋打個推字呀<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aa41b95ef4710b11c66fbc74c0f5d034deedd5","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c179f5ac049e8df267de5bdef32fa46f42a8a0c1","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d004ed94b75ab278237f1a3926ed5ce0fc5d99bb","tid":1359442,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"有時太長又密影響埋睇其他reply<br />\n我覺得可以整啲簡短/排板好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如唔好紅字大字"},{"pid":"d743cc9490c6932de02b815c5a19a92d8c7331b0","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d004ed94b75ab278237f1a3926ed5ce0fc5d99bb","tid":1359442,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"有時太長又密影響埋睇其他reply<br />\n我覺得可以整啲簡短/排板好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如唔好紅字大字"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"所以一句起兩句止都好夠<br />\n例如五大訴求入面揀一樣你認為最重要嘅出嚟去推post<br />\n<blockquote>回應五大訴求！<strong>特別係成立獨立調查委員會！</strong></blockquote><br />\n又或者好似我咁<br />\n用「光復香港，時代革命」嚟推post<br />\n點都好過個推字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df0ef9ea0d430ed5b7f2af2c5a1a2a9b04b86c","tid":1359442,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike"